Title: Os desafios da implantação da Base Nacional Comum Curricular (BNCC) no Brasil: uma revisão de literatura
Title: Os desafios da implantação da Base Nacional Comum Curricular (BNCC) no Brasil: uma revisão de literatura
Creator(s): Moura, M. O., & Ferreira, W. J. A.
Description: This article presents a critical analysis of the challenges of the implementation of the Common National Curriculum Base (BNCC) in Brazil. The analysis was carried out from the perspective of the challenges to be faced in the process of implantation and the possible scenarios for the inclusion of this policy. Theoretical and empirical aspects were analyzed. The main challenges were found in the field of planning, implementation and evaluation of the BNCC. The authors conclude that the implementation of the BNCC should be based on a shared vision of the content to be included and that the perspectives of the actors involved with the process must be taken into account to overcome the challenges. The main difficulties are related to the aspects of implementation, inclusion of the actors and evaluation.
